        newexpr = replace(newexpr,") & Helper.Secondary"," | SpecSource.arMPSGGESP) & Helper.Secondary",0)

        ~ Now replace the old expresson with our modified one
        linkage[table].field[cCstS2Expr].text = newexpr]]></eval>
    </thing>
