      ~ If we're disabled, do nothing
      doneif (tagis[Helper.FtDisable] <> 0)

      hero.child[Initiative].field[Bonus].value += 2]]></eval>
    </thing>
  <thing id="cMPSGGEmpa" name="Empathy" description="The sensitive has a knack for being aware of the feelings and thoughts of others without having those feelings and thoughts communicated in any objectively explicit manner, giving them an advantage during interactions.\n\n{b}Benefit{/b}: An innate talent provides a bonus on checks involving Bluff, Diplomacy, Handle Animal, Intimidate, Perform, and Sense Motive provided they spend at least 1 minute observing their target prior to making the skill check. \n\n{b}Special{/b}: The bonus is equal to half the Sensitive&apos;s class level (minimum +1)." compset="CustomSpec" summary="Bonus on checks involving interaction skills" uniqueness="unique">
    <comment/>
    <usesource source="MPRGGAnac"/>
