  <thing id="cMPSGGIUDe" name="Improved Uncanny Dodge" description="{b}Benefit{/b}: The sensitive can no longer be flanked. This defense denies an attacker with sneak attack the ability to use sneak attack on the sensitive when flanking her. Attackers with at least four more levels in classes that grant sneak attack than the sensitive has levels in classes that grant uncanny dodge may still use sneak attack when flanking." compset="CustomSpec" summary="The sensitive can no longer be flanked." uniqueness="unique">
    <comment/>
    <usesource source="MPRGGAnac"/>
