  <thing id="cMPSGGOWEv" name="One With Everything" description="The sensitive can communicate with any creature with an Int of 2 or more as if she spoke its native tongue (even if it does not itself have a language), and is automatically treated as taking 20 on any Sense Motive check.  \n\n{b}Benefit{/b}: At 20th level, a sensitive&apos;s understanding of the universe makes her part of all creatures, places, and things. \n\nAdditionally, the sensitive&apos;s self-awareness is so great she becomes immune to all mind-affecting effects." compset="CustomSpec" summary="Can communicate with any creature with an Int of 2 or more" uniqueness="unique">
